      "body" : "> the code and issue tracking is [confusingly](https://github.com/boostorg/process/pull/243) spread across multiple repositories, see https://github.com/boostorg/process/ and https://github.com/klemens-morgenstern/boost-process), which themselves each have different versions of the code\r\n\r\nThis is no longer the case.\r\n\r\nAnd Boost [Process V2](https://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_80_0_beta1/doc/html/boost_process/v2.html) is coming.",
